# SYS-Agent Project Context

## Identity

This directory (`{{PROJECT_ROOT}}`) is a project-specific operational repo derived from the SACST template for the `{{INSTANCE_NAME}}` environment.

## Rules

1. This repo is allowed to contain environment-specific context.
2. This repo is expected to evolve for the managed environment.
3. This repo must not write back into the SACST template repo directly.
4. Template improvements flow through explicit sync from SACST.
5. Vendor/OS command research, credential references, and full-spectrum operator-gated security scope belong in this project repo, not in SACST.
6. Raw credentials, private keys, tokens, certificates, and private full configs must stay outside normal repo files and logs.
